<h1>counter @KJ{{person}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<p>

<table class="highlight">
<tr> <td> 1  </td> <td class="irregular"> @HI{{hitori}}</td>      <td> @KJ{{one^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 2  </td> <td class="irregular"> @HI{{futari}}</td>      <td> @KJ{{two^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 3  </td> <td>                   @HI{{sannninn}}</td>    <td> @KJ{{three^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 4  </td> <td class="irregular"> @HI{{yoninn}}</td>      <td> @KJ{{four^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 5  </td> <td>                   @HI{{goninn}}</td>      <td> @KJ{{five^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 6  </td> <td>                   @HI{{rokuninn}}</td>    <td> @KJ{{six^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 7  </td> <td>                   @HI{{nananinn}}</td>    <td> @KJ{{seven^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 8  </td> <td>                   @HI{{hachininn}}</td>   <td> @KJ{{eight^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 9  </td> <td>                   @HI{{kyuuninn}}</td>    <td> @KJ{{nine^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> 10 </td> <td>                   @HI{{juuninn}}</td>     <td> @KJ{{ten^person}} </td></tr>
<tr> <td> ?  </td> <td>                   @HI{{nannninn}}</td>    <td> &nbsp; </td></tr>
</table>
</p>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
This counter is used to count people.
</p>
<p>
To ask "how many people?", use @HI{{nannninn}}.
</p>

